d:
Hey there!
A big thank you to everyone for your feedback, it's always a real pleasure to read your comments!
Feel free to keep sharing your thoughts, it helps a lot and motivates me every step of the way.

And now, I’m excited to announce the release of Heat on Stream a comics set in the KPop Demon Hunters universe, I hope you’ll enjoy this One-shot! I might have had a bit too many ideas for this one. I probably should have released it in two separate parts, but let’s say it’s a special end-of-year treat.

The full comic is now available to everyone! I'm thrilled to share it with you all.
The next project is scheduled for release at the end of the month.
Also, the poll to decide which project I’ll work on next will go live tomorrow! If you'd like to participate, consider joining my SubscribeStar page.

And if you want to keep up with my kinky projects, you can follow me here: https://x.com/SAX__kun
Or, if you want to support my work, you can join me on SubscribeStar: https://subscribestar.adult/sax_kun ❤️
